Brazil, September 17-October 22. All games played in Río de Janeiro.

17.09.22  Río de Janeiro, das Laranjeiras
BRA - CHI 1:1 (1:1)
(30,000) Ricardo Vallarino URU
BRA: Marcos - Palamone, Bartô - Laís, Amílcar, Fortes - Formiga, Neco, Friedenreich, Tatú,Rodrigues I
CHI: Bernal - Vergara, Poirier - Elgueta, Catalán, González - Abello, Domínguez, Bravo,Encina, Varas
1:0 Tatú 9, 1:1 Bravo 41

