NOTE: the uruguayans renounced to the final play-off tournament due to the dreadful performance of the brazilian referee.

15.10.22  Río de Janeiro, das Laranjeiras
BRA - ARG 2:0 (1:0)
(25,000) Francisco Andreu PAR
BRA: Kuntz - Palamone, Bartô - Laís, Amílcar, Fortes - Formiga, Neco, Héitor Domingues,Tatú, Rodrigues I
ARG: Tesoriere - A.Celli, Sarasíbar - Chabrolín, Médici, Solari - Rivet, Libonatti,Gaslini, E.Celli, Francia
1:0 Neco 42, 2:0 Amílcar 86 p

18.10.22  Río de Janeiro, das Laranjeiras
ARG - PAR 2:0 (0:0)
(8,000) Enrique Vignal BRA
ARG: Tesoriere - A.Celli, Sarasíbar - Chabrolín, Médici, Solari - Rivet, De Césari,Gaslini, E.Celli, Francia
PAR: Denis - Mena Porta, Paredes - Centurión Miranda, Fleitas Solich, Benítez Casco -Schaerer, Capdevila, López, Rivas, Erico
1:0 Francia 63, 2:0 Francia 79 p
NOTE: PAR left the field in the 79th minute in protest against the penalty sanctioned by the referee. Only Denis stayed in the field, but failed to save the shot.
NOTE: As URU withdrew, playoff needed between BRA and PAR to decide the champion.


Final

22.10.22  Río de Janeiro, das Laranjeiras
BRA - PAR 3:0 (1:0)
(20,000) Servando Pérez ARG
BRA: Kuntz - Palamone, Bartô - Laís, Amílcar, Fortes - Formiga, Neco,Héitor Domingues, Tatú, Rodrigues I
PAR: Denis - González, Paredes - Centurión Miranda, Fleitas Solich,Benítez Casco - Schaerer, Capdevila, López, Rivas, Fretes
1:0 Neco 11, 2:0 Formiga 48, 3:0 Formiga 89




